{"tid":2180603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"常春藤名校華裔生無視防疫開派對 逾3000人聯署促踢出校","createTime":"2020-08-30T03:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T04:33:55.000Z","uid":225931,"like":44,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f700a299e357c21d1021395b18db4258b7a5a4b0","tid":2180603,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"一群康乃爾大學學生在網上發起聯署，指控Jessica Zhang不遵守防疫規定，為一己私利而置公眾健康於不顧，行為不符合康乃爾學生的價值，認為她影衰學校（a horrible representation）。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，必須向做出這種行動的學生追究，她公開展示這種行為，意味她無須當康乃爾學生，直指她肆意危害本地學生，損害學校聲譽，促校方對違反防疫規定的人採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Jessica Zhang在學校並不算十分知名，卻是網絡名人，她的TikTok帳戶追隨者數目多達55萬；她的影片內容，主要與大學校園生活有關，分享如何寫論文、申請獎學金、讀書及省錢要訣等內容。<br />\n<br />\nJessica Zhang正於校外酒店接受隔離，她回應事件時指，有關聯署散播不實資訊，是對她品格的不公平抹黑，她稱校方已與她聯絡，表明聯署不會影響對她的處分。<br />\n<br />\n她並提到自身背景，指自己來自重視子女教育的<strong>中國</strong>移民家庭，自小非常努力，才成功入讀康乃爾大學，若因一個錯誤，毀掉自己的事業，她會非常沮喪（devastated）。"},{"pid":"4b81810ac55649b58f3a016cf0340443049f6a9b","tid":2180603,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a219b9439d4410bee8c70f7c15f23ace5f4e2131","tid":2180603,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bfdad5b4ce410893dc50937f52bfd918af359b","tid":2180603,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislik